Package com.project

Class Project

java.lang.Object
com.project.Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
IProject
public class Project extends Object implements IProject
The Project class represents a housing project with details about units, pricing, dates, and personnel. This class implements the IProject interface and manages project visibility, applications, and inquiries.
